Even help from Tamayo and Yushiro may not be enough to defeat these demons who claim to belong to the Twelve Kizuki that directly serve Kibutsuji, the demon responsible for all of Tanjiroâ€™s woes! But if these demons can be defeated, what secrets can they reveal about Kibutsuji? -- VIZ Media
